%% F11 — Architecture (data-flow diagram)
%% Owner: F11-T01
%% Mostra o pipeline completo de /elicit-prd: leitura do question template,
%% loop interativo via AskUserQuestion, escrita do draft em
%% claude-didio-out/, confirmação e cópia para tasks/features/.../_brief.md.

flowchart LR
    User(["👤 User"])

    subgraph Orchestrator["Orchestrator (model que invocou /elicit-prd)"]
        CMD["/elicit-prd FXX &quot;título&quot;"]
        LOAD["Load question template"]
        ASK["Loop: AskUserQuestion (or text fallback)"]
        WRITE["Write draft (template.md format)"]
        CONFIRM["AskUserQuestion: copy to brief?"]
        COPY["Copy draft → _brief.md"]
        HINT["Suggest: /plan-feature FXX"]
    end

    subgraph FS["File system"]
        QT[("templates/docs/prd/<br/>elicit-questions.md<br/>(8 fixed + 2 conditional Qs)")]
        TPL[("templates/docs/prd/<br/>template.md<br/>(PRD output format — referenced)")]
        DRAFT[("claude-didio-out/prd-drafts/<br/>FXX-prd.md<br/>(gitignored, preserved)")]
        BRIEF[("tasks/features/FXX-slug/<br/>_brief.md")]
    end

    User -->|invokes| CMD
    CMD --> LOAD
    LOAD -->|reads| QT
    LOAD --> ASK
    ASK <-->|each Q| User
    ASK -->|skip → placeholder| WRITE
    ASK -->|answer → value| WRITE
    WRITE -->|format from| TPL
    WRITE -->|writes| DRAFT
    DRAFT --> CONFIRM
    CONFIRM <-->|yes/no| User
    CONFIRM -->|yes| COPY
    COPY -->|reads| DRAFT
    COPY -->|creates| BRIEF
    COPY --> HINT
    CONFIRM -->|no| HINT
    HINT -->|prints| User

    classDef store fill:#e3e3ff,stroke:#5050aa
    class QT,TPL,DRAFT,BRIEF store
